10年過去.....我都係最近先知,10個都係9個去個間COMXX買貨<br />\n3-4年一大爆,唔係老母板燒,就係DISPLAY爆<br />\n心諗...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌....我個陣乜撚都唔識(呢家好少少) 濕左部9600GE DIS同奔騰U既垃圾機都用到呢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲比佢地串過玩乜OLG,結果WOWS我都入到去玩...佢地年年都係度煩3年一爆4年保養...<br />\n<br />\n都係個句:<br />\n砌機...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係幾頭痕既野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbca691b3e447c8af64648fb497b2ec510b9a07f","tid":269491,"uid":1888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Amd cpu...砍掉重練吧</blockquote><br />\namd都係廢？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 有ryzen</blockquote><br />\n以前舊底既AMD係堅廢<br />\n係ryzen系列先後上"},{"pid":"19b6b85d0a7fb86eb0c8c01943e8105ee44e6b8e","tid":269491,"uid":45712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪兩年都冇裝過driver</blockquote><br />\n裝咩driver<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係講笑，<a href=\"http://nvidia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnvidia.com&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=65cd794a\" target=\"_blank\">http://nvidia.com</a>應該幫倒你</blockquote><br />\n我有裝呢個"},{"pid":"10a1c8930bf1ea74cd38e34a1388c9463fe71008","tid":269491,"uid":45712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我七年前砌460打LOL都順<br />\n長期100+fps<br />\n笑死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉我屌 係我太笨7"},{"pid":"e71a672b564209148e2c2b35e274db0cf32fc102","tid":269491,"uid":45712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保用3年<i